ANALYSIS OF CONSOLIDATED SALES

IN 2016, WORLDWIDE SALES INCREASED 2.6% TO $71.9 BILLION, COMPARED TO A DECREASE OF 5.7% IN 2015 AND AN INCREASE OF 4.2% IN 2014. THESE SALES CHANGES CONSISTED OF THE FOLLOWING.

