IN 2016, ACQUISITIONS AND DIVESTITURES HAD A NEGATIVE IMPACT OF 1.1% ON THE WORLDWIDE OPERATIONAL SALES GROWTH AND COMPETITIVE PRODUCTS TO THE COMPANY'S HEPATITIS C PRODUCTS, OLYSIO

