OF EMPLOYEE SEVERANCE. APPROXIMATELY ONE HALF OF THE CUMULATIVE PRE-TAX COSTS ARE NON-CASH, RELATING PRIMARILY TO FACILITY RATIONALIZATION, INVENTORY WRITE-OFFS AND INTANGIBLE ASSET WRITE-OFFS.

